    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei aeterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21"
                            >Berengarius</persName> divina favente clementia <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >rex</rs>. Si sacris et venerabilibus locis temporalia et transitoria
                        impendimus, eterna et sine fine mansura nos auxiliante Domino adipisci
                        nequaquam difidimus. Quapropter omnium [fidelium] sancte Dei Ecclesie
                        nostrorumque presentium scilicet et futurorum noverit industria, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Marquis/duke"><name ref="Adalardus"
                            >Adelardum</name></persName> illustrem <rs key="#Marquis/duke"
                            >marchionem</rs> dilectissimum <rs key="#fidelisOf">fidelem nostrum</rs>
                        nostram suppliciter exorasse <rs key="#Intercessory">clementiam</rs>,
                        quatenus <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> in honore <orgName
                            key="#Houses #Islands #Curtes #Domuscultae #Mansi #Landed_possessions #Mills #Churches #Royal_slave #Private_foundations"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/211">sancti Iohannis</orgName> intra hanc
                            <placeName ref="#places/65">Ticinensem civitatem</placeName> fundate
                        dignaremur concedere, confirmare et corroborare sub plenissima integritate
                        omnes res et possessiones quas ipsa ecclesia Sancti Iohannis tam per <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio">donum</rs> sanctae memorie <persName
                            key="#Queen" ref="#people/299">Gondiperge</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">reginae</rs>, que <rs key="#Private_foundations">ipsam
                            edificavit ecclesiam</rs>, quam per <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            >precepta regum et imperatorum</rs> seu et firmitates aliorum
                        religiosorum hominum actenus habere et detinere dinoscitur. Cuius precibus
                        aclinati, ita fieri anuimus, huius nostre concessionis et confirmationis
                        preceptum scribi iubentes, [per quod] prenominate ecclesie Sancti Iohannis
                        concedimus, confirmamus et sub omni integritate coroboramus omnes res et
                        possessiones suas quas priscis temporibus tenuit et possedit, eo videlicet
                        ordine, ut ipsa ecclesia omnes res et possessiones suas, quas sibi per donum
                        prenominate regine et per precepta antecessorum nostrorum regum videlicet et
                        imperatorum et firmitates aliorum bonorum hominum possidere cernitur,
                        deinceps per hoc nostrum preceptum cum omni sua integritate teneat et
                        pleniter possideat, tam eas <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >res et possessiones que ad partem publicam regni nostri pertinuerunt
                            quam et illas quas nostri antecessores</rs>, reges videlicet et
                        imperatores per sua precepta ob amorem Dei et sancti Iohannis <rs
                            key="#Canons">canonicis</rs> in ipsa ecclesia Deo militantibus ad victum
                        et vestimentum specialiter tribuerunt et denominative concesserunt,
                        videlicet infra menia huius Ticinensis [civitatis] <rs key="#Churches"
                            >capellam</rs> unam <orgName
                            key="#Houses #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            >Sancti Victoris</orgName> constructam cum <rs key="#Houses">solario
                            ante se et solariolum unum</rs> post tribunal prope cortem <geogName
                            key="#Houses #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/304"><placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Palatiolum</placeName></geogName>, <rs key="#Houses">mansiones
                            duas</rs> penes cortem <geogName
                            key="#Houses #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/305"><placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Genuensem</placeName></geogName>, <rs key="#Houses">salatiolum
                            unum</rs> ante portam eiusdem ecclesie, <rs key="#Houses">mansiones
                            duas</rs>, claustra in circuitu ecclesie cum viridatio extra muros
                        civitatis, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">hortulos duos</rs> prope
                            <orgName>basilicam Sancti Victoris</orgName>, <rs>clausuram unam</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Landed_possessions">campos tres</rs>, infra menia ipsius
                        civitatis <rs key="#Landed_possessions">braidam unam</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/634">Nassaria</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratellos quinque</rs>, in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Forests #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/635">Terra Arsa</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratum unum</rs> simul cum <rs key="#Forests"
                            >silvula</rs>, in <placeName ref="#places/709">Monteferrato</placeName>
                        in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Islands #Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/636">Rivassi</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">mansos quinque</rs> cum <rs key="#Islands">insula infra
                            Padum</rs>, <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/637">in Altruelini</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">absentem unum</rs>, <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/638">in Bertesassi</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">absentem unum</rs>, <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/639">in Pulveria</placeName><rs key="#Mansi"> mansum
                            unum</rs>, <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/640">in Bucellade</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">mansum unum</rs>, <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/641">in Gebedi</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">mansum unum</rs>, in loco qui nuncupatur <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/642">Archidiaconi</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">mansos septem</rs>, <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/643">in Balbiano</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Houses #Fundi #Landed_possessions" ref="#places/43">civitate
                            Placentina</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Houses">salatiolam unam</rs> cum <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables"
                            >parvo horto</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">campo uno</rs>, in
                        loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Domuscultae #Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            ref="#places/644">Sancti Cipriani</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Churches">capellam unam</rs> cum <rs key="#Domuscultae">domo
                            coltili</rs> et <rs key="#Mansi">mansos quatuor</rs> et cum omni sua
                        pertinentia, <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/645">in Segestri</placeName> quandam <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">absentem terram</rs>, similiter <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/646">in Levarnia</placeName> et <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/647">in Caurani</placeName> ac infra civitatem <placeName
                            ref="#places/626">Genuesam</placeName> et in <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/306">comitatu <placeName ref="#places/627"
                                >Terdonensi</placeName></geogName>, similiter in loco ubi dicitur
                            <placeName ref="#places/648">Regiana</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/649">Mariana</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/650">Verlasca</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/651">Freneto</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/652">Cassiano</placeName>, nec non et <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/653">Topiole</placeName>, in <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/307">comitatu <placeName ref="#places/628"
                                >Aquensi</placeName></geogName> in loco ubi dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/654">Cuspiano</placeName> cum omni sua integritate, in
                            <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/655">Cavanasco</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">mansos tres et absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/656">Frisosco</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/657">Bibiano</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/658">Miolaco</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Mills #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/659">Gambaro</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">mansos duos</rs> cum <rs key="#Mills">molendino</rs>, in
                            <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/660">Moliana</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">manentem unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/661">Corliasco</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/662">Merlade</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/664">Visedano</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/663">Carponio</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/665">Frontinassi</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/666">Grameneto</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/667">Turredano</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mansi">mansum unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Petiae #Wine #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/668">Aurello</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Wine">petias de vitibus duas</rs> et <rs key="#Petiae">campellum
                            unum</rs>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Districtio #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#estates/311">cortem de <placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Districtio #Royal_slave"
                                >Robationico</placeName></geogName> cum omnibus
                        pertinentiis suis et <rs key="#Royal_slave">familiis utriusque sexus</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Districtio">districtionibus</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/669">Carvina</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Royal_aldius">aldiones</rs> reddentes ceram ad luminaria prefate
                        ecclesie, similiter in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/670">Pino</placeName> et in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/671">Canobio</placeName>, hec solumodo usui et utilitati
                        canonicorum pretaxate ecclesie que nuncupatur Domnarum, sicut alii nostri
                        antecessores reges et imperatores per sua precepta et alii religiosi et
                        sancti viri per suas firmitates concesserunt, in et nos per hoc nostrum
                        preceptum concedimus, confirmamus et pleniter coroboramus et perdonamus, ea
                        videlicet ratione, ut tam <persName key="#Archpriests"><name ref="Agibertus"
                                >Agevertus</name></persName> ipsius ecclesie <rs key="#Archpriests"
                            >archipresbiter</rs> et prepositus sibique subditi canonici quam et
                        eorum successores qui ibi pro tempore fuerint hec per huius nostre
                        auctoritatis donativum teneant ac possideant et exinde integram potestatem
                        habeant faciendi quicquid voluerint more ceterorum canonicorum, quatenus in
                        nostra mercede Deo et sancto Iohanni securi valeant deservire. Et si ipse
                        archipresbiter et prepositus vel successores eiusdem ecclesie ab hac luce
                        migraverit, non aliunde sed ex sinu ispius ecclesie sibi archipresbiterum et
                        prepositum eligant. Reliqua omnia ad eandem ecclesiam pertinentia pars
                        publica regni nostri per hoc nostrum pracmaticum pleniter teneat et cum omni
                        integritate possideat, sua omnium hominum inquietudine et contradictione
                        remota. Si quis igitur huius nostre concessionis et confirmationis preceptum
                        infringere vel violare aliquando presumpserit, sciat se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras ducentum</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis"
                            >medietatem camere palatii nostri</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem parti ipsius
                            ecclesie Sancti Iohannis</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur diligentiusque ab
                        omnibus observetur, manu propria roborantes de anulo nostro subter iussimus
                        insigniri. Signum (M) domni Berengarii gloriosissimi regis. <persName
                            key="#Chancellor" ref="#people/1501">Iohannes</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/216">Ardingi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. Data non. Kal. Iul.,
                        anno dominice incarnationis DCCCCVIIII, anno vero domni Berengarii
                        gloriosissimi regis XXII, indictione duodecima, Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/65">Papie</placeName> palatii. In Christi nomine feliciter,
                        amen.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
